sentences.english: He also began to carry it out as soon as he took charge of FengXi warlord.
sentences.chinese: 在掌控奉系军阀统治权后，他也开始践行这一思想。

sentences.english: So, find out what it is that you want to be practicing.
sentences.chinese: 所以，首先应该搞明白什么是你想要践行的。

sentences.english: Moral models were apotheosis practising moral criterion in any times.
sentences.chinese: 道德典范是任何时代践行道德规范的楷模。

sentences.english: Constructing the harmonious campus culture is concrete fulfillment for constructing harmonious university.
sentences.chinese: 建设和谐的校园文化，是构建和谐大学的具体践行。

sentences.english: The more you live these commandments, the more His spirit can rest with you.
sentences.chinese: 愈是能够践行这“两大诫命”，圣灵愈是与你同在。

sentences.english: The implementation of the scientific outlook of development should adhere to humanism.
sentences.chinese: 当前科学发展观的践行，亦应坚持以人为本的精神。

sentences.english: People who use the principles say they work.
sentences.chinese: 践行了这些信条的人们都说管用。

sentences.english: So, practice good defensive design on all of them.
sentences.chinese: 所以，所有这些页面都要好好地践行防护性设计。

sentences.english: Guardiola adopted the measure to be in charge only of the First Divison team of Barcelona.
sentences.chinese: 瓜迪奥拉在自己成为一队教练后也践行着一个原则。

sentences.english: Women with great virtue in Shandong practiced the concept of virtue in different ways.
sentences.chinese: 山东守贞女性通过不同的行为模式践行其贞节观。
